The denunciation runs in the foreign press and two brave national columns. The detained reappear in eleven days, thinner, at a prison that had no record of them, now suddenly equipped with paperwork. A collection replaces the machine inside a month — a German model this time, heavier, harder to carry down stairs in boxes. The state teaches by raid; the Party learns by inventory.
